Selenium

A Collection of Different Elements to Play With

Alerts Explore the 3 types of JavaScript alerts! Drag and Drop Drag the ball around! Dynamic Attributes Attributes that change on refresh! Dynamic Content Content updates every 2s Dynamic Controls Elements that change state! File Upload Test your file uploads! Iframeception A page in a page in a page! Iframes A page in a page! Keyboard Events Use your keyboard here! Lazy Loading Elements that appear upon scrolling! Login Form Please sign in! Mouse Events Use your mouse here! Popups Work with popups! Selects Dropdowns and Multi Selects! Simple Form Enter data into a webpage! Sliders Slider elements! Tables Table elements! Tabs Launch new tabs by clicking a button! Target Practice Practice element targetting here! To-Do List Elements get added at runtime!
